24 payments shall not be suspended for a retired member who is reemployed if he or
25 she anticipates that he or she will receive less than the maximum permissible
26 earnings as provided by the Federal Social Security Act in compensation as a result
27 of reemployment during the calendar year. The payments shall be suspended at the
